            "value": "%3Cp%3EPrayer%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20godly%20society.%20Paul%20admonished%20us%20to%20offer%20prayers%20for%20kings%20and%20all%20those%20in%20authority.%20When%20we%20pray%20for%20our%20rulers%2C%20they%20become%20softened%20to%20the%20purposes%20of%20God%2C%20respectful%20to%20the%20Church%2C%20and%20honest%20and%20just%20in%20their%20lawmaking.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20peaceful%20and%20quiet%20society%20is%20the%20best%20environment%20in%20which%20the%20lost%20may%20be%20saved.%20When%20Satan%20is%20influencing%20government%2C%20wicked%20laws%20are%20passed%2C%20anarchy%20rules%2C%20and%20the%20Church%20is%20persecuted.%20Preaching%20the%20Word%2C%20printing%20Bibles%2C%20and%20establishing%20churches%20are%20forbidden%20in%20that%20environment.%20%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20our%20Savior%20%22wants%20everyone%20to%20be%20saved%20and%20to%20understand%20the%20truth%22%20(1%20Timothy%202%3A%204).%20He%20sent%20His%20Son%20as%20a%20ransom%20for%20all%20men%20and%20women%20(v.%206)%2C%20and%20thus%20He%20desires%20nations%20to%20be%20open%20to%20the%20preaching%20of%20the%20Gospel.%20Whenever%20we%20come%20together%20with%20other%20believers%2C%20we%20should%20pray%20specifically%20for%20each%20nation%20and%20ruler%20%22with%20holy%20hands%20lifted%20up%20to%20God%2C%20free%20from%20anger%20and%20controversy%22%20(v.%208).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20praying%20church%2C%20an%20open%20government%2C%20a%20perfect%20sacrifice%2C%20and%20an%20obedient%20preacher%20will%20bring%20the%20Gospel%20to%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20earth%20and%20usher%20in%20Jesus'%20return%20to%20reap%20the%20harvest!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
