            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2030%3A1-31%3A26%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_30_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPromises%20of%20Deliverance%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20another%20message%20to%20Jeremiah.%20He%20said%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_30_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20Write%20down%20for%20the%20record%20everything%20I%20have%20said%20to%20you%2C%20Jeremiah.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_30_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20time%20is%20coming%20when%20I%20will%20restore%20the%20fortunes%20of%20my%20people%20of%20Israel%20and%20Judah.%20I%20will%20bring%20them%20home%20to%20this%20land%20that%20I%20gave%20to%20their%20ancestors%2C%20and%20they%20will%20possess%20it%20again.%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_30_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20message%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20concerning%20Israel%20and%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_30_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch